        "client_msg_id": "798891bb-8778-445a-b443-e0584ccaa4d9",
        "type": "message",
        "text": "Because I'm now very concerned about culture fit, I ask the applicant to review our vision and core values, then, do a 300-500 draft on what it means to them and how they think they fit in. \n\nThat's before we book a call. \n\nNext, if what they send in and our first call is positive, I send them a very strategic piece, tell them to consume it and come up with 2 strategy-level content ideas that'll appeal to 2 of our ICPs. Of course, we've nailed our ICPs down to how we effect change in their lives, so this helps.\n\nI offer $100 for this 2nd assignment, so I do my best to only get very interesting prospects to this 2nd stage. \n\nAnd the goal of all this is to spot those who can think deeply and truly connect the dots between content strategy, our business, and our ICPs.",
        "user": "UUVRX9C13",
        "ts": "1626463948.488400",
